{"doc":" 告警与事故管理控制器（模块14）。\n\n <p>提供告警规则、告警事件的完整 CRUD 接口。</p>\n","fields":[],"enumConstants":[],"methods":[{"name":"listRules","paramTypes":["java.lang.String","java.lang.Long"],"doc":"查询告警规则列表（支持 scope/projectId 过滤）。 "},{"name":"createRule","paramTypes":["com.aiplatform.backend.entity.AlertRule"],"doc":"创建告警规则。 "},{"name":"updateRule","paramTypes":["java.lang.Long","com.aiplatform.backend.entity.AlertRule"],"doc":"编辑告警规则。 "},{"name":"updateRuleStatus","paramTypes":["java.lang.Long","java.util.Map"],"doc":"启用/禁用告警规则。 "},{"name":"listEvents","paramTypes":["java.lang.String","java.lang.String","int","int"],"doc":"查询告警事件列表（分页，支持 status/severity 过滤）。 "},{"name":"acknowledge","paramTypes":["java.lang.Long"],"doc":"确认告警（FIRING → ACKNOWLEDGED）。 "},{"name":"resolve","paramTypes":["java.lang.Long"],"doc":"解决告警（→ RESOLVED）。 "}],"constructors":[]}